<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Payment Failed</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
        background-color: #fff3f3;
        color: #b00020;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        padding-top: 50px;
      }
      .container {
        background: #fff;
        border: 2px solid #ffcdd2;
        border-radius: 10px;
        padding: 30px 40px;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(255, 0, 0, 0.1);
        max-width: 500px;
        width: 90%;
      }
      h1 {
        color: #d32f2f;
        font-size: 28px;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }
      ul {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
      }
      li {
        padding: 8px 0;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #f8bbd0;
      }
      .fail-icon {
        font-size: 48px;
        color: #e53935;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="fail-icon">‚ùå</div>
      <h1>Payment Failed</h1>
      <p>Unfortunately, your payment could not be processed.</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Transaction Ref No:</strong> <%= txnRefNo %></li>
        <li><strong>JazzCash Transaction ID:</strong> <%= transactionID %></li>
        <li><strong>Status:</strong> Failed</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Please try again or contact support if the issue persists.</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
